		___
		### Lua Examples
		#### Example 1
		Gets the current position on the path as a Vector.
		
		```lua 
		path:GetPositionOnPath( path:GetCursorPosition() )
		```
    **/
    
    function GetPositionOnPath(distance:Float):Vector;
    
    
    /**
